<strong>
Share this job:
</strong>
<input readonly="" class="share-job-copy-paste" type="text" value="https://remoteok.com/remote-jobs/remote-smb-sales-director-inside-sales-bamboohr-144200?ref=sh" style="">
 <br>
<span style="font-size:12px;margin-top:-7px;display:block;">Get a <a style="" href="https://rok.co">rok.co</a> short link</span>
</p>
