<h1 style="text-align:left;">
<span style="font-weight: 400;">Commit is hiring a </span><br>Remote Senior Full Stack Developer </h1>
<div class="html"><h2 dir="ltr"><br></h2><h2 dir="ltr"><strong>Not all jobs are the same, so why is every job description the same? Commit is <em>different</em> because we know every software developer out there is <em>different</em>.&nbsp;</strong></h2><p><strong><br></strong></p><p dir="ltr">If you’re a<strong> Senior Full-Stack Developer </strong>searching for your next startup role, we’ve got you covered! We work with over 90 pre-vetted impactful startups in North America who are building innovative solutions to ambitious problems.&nbsp;</p><p><strong><br></strong></p><p dir="ltr">Wondering what skills you need? <strong>If you have experience with a combination of the following tech stack <em>(not all!)</em>, we’d love to hear from you!</strong></p><ul><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr">FE: One/some of: Vue.js, React, Redux, Next</p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr">BE: One/some of: Node.js, Go/Golang, Python/Django/Flask, Ruby/Rails, Java/Scala, Rust</p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr">Understanding of DevOps: MongoDB, AWS, GCP, Docker, Kubernetes/Terraform, CI/CD</p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr">Understanding of RESTful APIs and/or GraphQL</p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr">Understanding of cloud-native distributed systems and microservices</p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr">Experience with relational databases, NoSQL databases, cloud infrastructure, product design</p></li></ul><p><strong><br></strong></p><p><strong>Get started with a few easy steps!</strong></p><ol><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr"><a rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" href="https://4xbxmmanuuz.typeform.com/to/czZWb1bn?utm_source=xxxxx&amp;utm_medium=xxxxx&amp;utm_campaign=xxxxx&amp;utm_term=xxxxx&amp;utm_content=xxxxx">Apply</a> on our website for a quicker response. Note: you must be located and eligible to work in Canada.</p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr">Attend a brief 3-step interview process with Commit. <a rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" href="https://docs.commit.dev/eps/ep-overview">Learn more</a>. Bonus: No technical interviews!</p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr">Got accepted? You’ll be paid a full salary while we work together to match you to a startup that best aligns with your values.</p></li><li dir="ltr"><p dir="ltr">Once matched, you pilot a startup for 3 months. If you love it, you can stay with them; if not, we’ll work with you to find a better match.</p></li></ol><p><br></p> Please mention the word <strong>SLEEK</strong> when applying to show you read the job post completely (#RMzQuMTcxLjEzMi4yMDc=). This is a feature to avoid fake spam applicants. Companies can search these words to find applicants that read this and instantly see they're human.<br>
